    "desc": "We’re a top 50 CPA firm delivering a full spectrum of services to help our clients overcome their financial and business challenges. Serving New York…",
    "navbar": "WHO WE SERVE\nWHAT WE DO\nMORE\nCLIENT PORTAL\nSUBMIT RFP\nCONTACT US",
    "text": "A Career & More. CLICK HERE to explore opportunities with TBG today!\nWHO WE SERVE\nWHAT WE DO\nMORE\nCLIENT PORTAL\nSUBMIT RFP\nCONTACT US\nTHE BONADIO GROUP\nYour Success\n& More.\nWe bring promise and\npurpose to all we do.\nMEET OUR TEAM\nOUR SERVICES\nBIG FIRM CAPABILITY. SMALL FIRM PERSONALITY.\nWhat We Do\nWe’re a top 50 CPA firm who delivers a full spectrum of services to help our clients overcome their financial and business challenges. We dive deep into each industry we serve to bring even more to the table with every engagement.\nACCOUNTING & AUDIT\nTAX\nCONSULTING & MORE\nOUTSOURCE ACCOUNTING & FINANCE\nINFORMATION RISK MANAGEMENT\nWEALTH MANAGEMENT\nOur Story\nCommitted to You.\nWe work hard to find the best solution for each individual client because we know that one size doesn’t fit all.\nBY THE NUMBERS\n40+\nYears in Business\n800+\nEmployees\n10\nLocations\n50\nTop 50 Accounting Firm\nLEARN MORE\nOUR CAREERS\nProblem Solvers. Industry Experts. Trusted Partners.\nOur clients look to us as trusted, strategic, community-oriented partners who have a deep knowledge of their business and priorities. Your success is the foundation for everything we do, for both our clients and in the communities they live.\nJOIN OUR TEAM\nOUR EXPERTISE\nIndustry-Leading Ideas\nCombining technical expertise with a keen understanding of our client’s businesses, we offer knowledgeable commentary on a broad spectrum of industry trends through written articles, in-person seminars, webinars, thought leadership & more.\nVIEW NEWS & EVENTS\nSUBSCRIBE\nGet the latest Bonadio news straight to your inbox.\nWe Always Strive to Give Our Clients More...\nWe strive to give our clients more:\nAs people\nAs problem solvers\nAs experts\nAs community leaders\nVIEW CLIENTS\nReady to talk? Let's get started.\nCONTACT US\nThe Bonadio Group is an independent firm of Moore North America, Inc., which is associated with the Moore Global Network Limited.\nWHO WE SERVE\nWHAT WE DO\nABOUT US\nNEWS & EVENTS\nINNOVATION\nOUR PEOPLE\nCAREERS\nEMAIL PREFERENCES\nCLIENT PORTAL\nSUBMIT RFP\nCONTACT US\nToll Free: (877) 917-3077\nThe Bonadio Group serves businesses in Buffalo, Rochester, Syracuse,\nAlbany, Utica, NYC, Dallas, Rutland & Beyond!\n© 2022 - BONADIO & CO., LLP, ALL RIGHTS RESERVED\n2020 PEER REVIEW REPORT PRIVACY POLICY TERMS OF USE ACCESSIBILITY\nWe use cookies and other technologies to optimize site functionally, analyze website traffic, and share information with our service and analytics partners. To view our Privacy Policy, which discusses cookies, click here. By continuing to use & browse our services, you agree to our Privacy Policy, our use of cookies, and the Terms and Conditions.\nOK\nMORE INFO",
